default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThe NHPP identifies eight measures, broad themes, which in turn are further subdivided into identifiable activities and cover all of our heritage protection activities these
default measures are – 
default      
defaultMeasure 1 – Foresight
defaultMeasure 2 - Threat: Assessment and Response
defaultMeasure 3 - Understanding: Recognition/Identification of the Resource
defaultMeasure 4 - Understanding: Assessment of Character and Significance
defaultMeasure 5 -
default Responses: Protecting Significance
defaultMeasure 6 - 
defaultManaging Change
defaultMeasure 7 - Responses: Protecting and Managing Major Historic Estates
defaultMeasure 8 - Responses: Help and Advice for Owners
